---
title: Seared Honey Salmon & Couscous Tabbouleh with Garlic Dip & Pumpkin Seeds
description: Couscous tabbouleh is a winning side dish – it’s fast, fresh and full of flavour. Serve it next to gently seared salmon and garlic dip,
plus add a sprinkling of roasted seeds for extra goodness and crunch. This meal is a star performer!
